Welcome

To a new partnership experience

Why choose us

Dedicated Affiliate Team

Always there when you need it most

Flexible Commissions

Variety of plans to choose from

Timely & Safe Payments

Variety of payment methods

Lifetime Rev Share

No negative carryover for all partners

Detailed Reporting

Your player stats within several clicks

Exceptional Monetization

Industry leading conversion & retention rates
Sign up now

Customised Commission Plans

We believe in recognizing your efforts and the value you bring to our casino and sports brands. That's why we offer customised commission plans, ensuring that every player that you bring becomes a lasting source of income. Rest assured, your hard work won't go unnoticed or unrewarded.

Our Brands

Our flagship casino and sports brand themed around making Kings of our players. With a bespoke acquisition and loyalty program focused on mega jackpots, players are awarded multiple opportunities daily to win big and join the ranks of the elite!

Events & Conferences

Check out the list of upcoming events that we will be attending. Don't forget to book a meeting with one of our affiliate teams to explore exciting partnership possibilities. Our team is eager to meet face-to-face, exchange insights and brainstorm ways to foster mutual growth and success. Let’s seize this opportunity to strengthen our bonds and make lasting strides together.

Sign up now

Meet The Team
